text: Main Gate Front VIew Government Shaheed Suhrawardy College ()is a public college Laxsmibazar near Bahadurshah Park of Old Dhaka, Bangladesh. It offers higher-secondary education (HSC). It has bachelor's degree and master's degree programs as well which divisions are affiliated to the University of Dhaka since 16 February 2017. ==References== Category:Organisations based in Dhaka Category:Education in Dhaka Category:Schools in Dhaka District Category:Educational institutions established in 1949 Category:1949 establishments in Pakistan
